1
00:00:15,767 --> 00:00:16,800
Rina, I did what you asked me
to do.

2
00:00:16,933 --> 00:00:19,267
I made a hole
in Lucho's car brakes.

3
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:20,233
Very good.

4
00:00:20,367 --> 00:00:22,333
I hope you didn't mess up
this time.

5
00:00:22,467 --> 00:00:25,233
His brakes won't be working
once they start driving the car.

6
00:00:25,367 --> 00:00:27,067
- Eden?
- Hurry, you have to go!

7
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:28,133
Hurry!

8
00:00:28,267 --> 00:00:29,267
Mom is there.

9
00:00:31,167 --> 00:00:33,333
- Yen!
- I knew it!

10
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:34,800
- Mom!
- Where are you going?

11
00:00:34,933 --> 00:00:35,867
Let me go!

12
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,867
No! You're not coming with him!

13
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,800
Ma'am Rina, I was going
to tell Sir Victor

14
00:00:41,933 --> 00:00:43,000
that Red had gone out.

15
00:00:43,133 --> 00:00:44,433
- What?
- Rina.

16
00:00:44,567 --> 00:00:46,633
Are you still outside
the Madrigals' property?

17
00:00:46,767 --> 00:00:48,833
No, I'm back in my cave now.

18
00:00:48,967 --> 00:00:50,267
Red isn't here.

19
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:51,733
What do you want me to do?

20
00:00:51,867 --> 00:00:52,767
Go back to their house.

21
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:53,867
Keep an eye on them.

22
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:58,067
Make sure Amanda won't hurt him.

23
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:02,033
Mom, we will fulfill our dream
of having our own family.

24
00:01:02,167 --> 00:01:03,267
No!

25
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,167
Dindi, where's your sister?

26
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:06,667
Help!

27
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,600
Help!

28
00:01:08,767 --> 00:01:10,000
Lucho!

29
00:01:10,133 --> 00:01:11,400
Lucho!

30
00:01:11,533 --> 00:01:12,567
Amanda!

31
00:01:19,433 --> 00:01:20,767
This is not my car key!

32
00:01:20,900 --> 00:01:22,633
Eden!

33
00:01:22,767 --> 00:01:24,100
Lucho!

34
00:01:24,233 --> 00:01:25,367
Follow them!

35
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:26,700
Let's follow them.

36
00:01:29,067 --> 00:01:31,033
- Where's my son?
- I've been standing out here.

37
00:01:31,167 --> 00:01:32,867
But I haven't seen Red.

38
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:35,400
But I saw Amanda
leave the house.

39
00:01:35,533 --> 00:01:37,667
Red, someone's following us.

40
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,633
Red, they're following us.

41
00:01:39,767 --> 00:01:41,667
- Drive faster!
- Drive faster!

42
00:01:41,833 --> 00:01:43,033
We can't overtake.

43
00:01:43,167 --> 00:01:44,967
- There are a lot of cars.
- Go on.

44
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:47,933
Just stay close to them.
Don't lose them.

45
00:01:48,067 --> 00:01:49,767
This is our chance to lose them.

46
00:01:53,567 --> 00:01:54,633
Overtake that truck!

47
00:02:00,433 --> 00:02:02,633
They didn't get to overtake
that truck.

48
00:02:02,767 --> 00:02:04,233
Go ahead, overtake them!

49
00:02:04,367 --> 00:02:08,367
If Red's car is still here,
but Lucho's car is gone...

50
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:11,600
they took Red with them
using their car!

51
00:02:11,733 --> 00:02:14,167
- What's the matter, Red?
- The break is not working.

52
00:02:14,333 --> 00:02:15,433
What are we going to do?

53
00:02:15,567 --> 00:02:17,367
I need to crash this car
somewhere to stop it.

54
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:20,067
- You can't do that!
- This is the only way.

55
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,533
What about you, Red?

56
00:02:21,667 --> 00:02:22,833
When I say jump.

57
00:02:22,967 --> 00:02:24,300
- You have to jump.
- I don't want to!

58
00:02:24,433 --> 00:02:26,300
- We have no other choice, Yen!
- I don't want to!

59
00:02:26,433 --> 00:02:27,633
- One...
- No!

60
00:02:27,767 --> 00:02:28,800
two,

61
00:02:28,933 --> 00:02:30,200
three!

62
00:02:30,333 --> 00:02:31,333
Go!

63
00:02:52,733 --> 00:02:56,067
We can't lose them!

64
00:03:04,467 --> 00:03:07,300
Lucho, we can't lose them.

65
00:03:07,433 --> 00:03:10,100
Red can't take Eden with him.

66
00:03:10,233 --> 00:03:11,967
I can't lose my daughter.

67
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:13,000
I know.

68
00:03:13,133 --> 00:03:14,800
Just relax.

69
00:03:14,933 --> 00:03:16,167
We'll find her.

70
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:20,333
Look around.

71
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:21,533
Keep on the lookout.

72
00:03:22,867 --> 00:03:23,900
I don't see the car.

73
00:03:36,267 --> 00:03:37,333
One!

74
00:03:39,133 --> 00:03:40,900
- Red, no!
- Two!

75
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,600
Three!

76
00:04:02,433 --> 00:04:04,133
Yen, the car brake
is not working.

77
00:04:04,267 --> 00:04:05,267
What?

78
00:04:06,833 --> 00:04:08,567
What are we going to do?

79
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:10,400
The only way to stop this car

80
00:04:10,533 --> 00:04:14,467
is I have to crash it somewhere,
Yen.

81
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:15,567
No, Red!

82
00:04:16,967 --> 00:04:18,533
Yen, this is the only way.

83
00:04:19,733 --> 00:04:21,300
What about you?

84
00:04:21,433 --> 00:04:22,800
What are you talking about? No!

85
00:04:22,933 --> 00:04:24,467
- I won't let you do this!
- Don't worry about me.

86
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,700
You have to save yourself, okay?

87
00:04:26,833 --> 00:04:28,433
When I say jump,
you have to jump.

88
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,367
- No, Red!
- We have no other choice!

89
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:32,300
- I don't want to, Red!
- You have to do what I say!

90
00:04:32,433 --> 00:04:33,400
You have to.

91
00:04:33,533 --> 00:04:35,000
- I don't want to!
- You have to do as I say.

92
00:04:35,133 --> 00:04:36,300
We don't have a choice.

93
00:04:37,367 --> 00:04:38,600
I won't let you do this.

94
00:04:41,333 --> 00:04:42,867
Red, what are you doing?

95
00:04:44,433 --> 00:04:45,833
Red, what are you doing?

96
00:04:47,767 --> 00:04:49,367
On the count of three, Yen.

97
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:50,700
- One!
- Red, no!

98
00:04:50,833 --> 00:04:51,900
Two!

99
00:04:52,033 --> 00:04:53,133
Three!

100
00:04:55,433 --> 00:04:56,367
Go!

101
00:06:12,167 --> 00:06:13,833
Red, wake up.

102
00:06:13,967 --> 00:06:15,333
Red, can you hear me?

103
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,600
Red?

104
00:06:17,733 --> 00:06:18,700
Red, wake up!

105
00:06:19,967 --> 00:06:20,967
Red!

106
00:06:21,100 --> 00:06:22,900
Red, wake up.

107
00:06:23,033 --> 00:06:24,233
Red, I'm here.

108
00:06:25,733 --> 00:06:26,800
Red, wake up.

109
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:31,367
Red.

110
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:33,100
Red, you can't leave me.

111
00:06:33,233 --> 00:06:35,267
Red! Red, you have to wake up.

112
00:06:37,233 --> 00:06:38,300
Red!

113
00:06:38,433 --> 00:06:39,700
Please wake up!

114
00:06:42,333 --> 00:06:43,433
Red!

115
00:06:46,533 --> 00:06:49,367
Red, I know you like
to joke around.

116
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:51,533
Please don't mess with me
right now.

117
00:06:55,033 --> 00:06:57,067
Red, please wake up.

118
00:07:02,333 --> 00:07:04,200
Please, wake up.

119
00:07:05,333 --> 00:07:07,267
Didn't you promise
we'd never be apart?

120
00:07:08,933 --> 00:07:10,567
You said we'd never give up.

121
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:13,333
Why are you giving up now?

122
00:07:13,467 --> 00:07:14,800
Red, wake up.

123
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:17,200
Red, wake up!

124
00:07:21,033 --> 00:07:23,233
Red, you have to wake up,
please.

125
00:07:25,267 --> 00:07:27,467
I can't live without you.

126
00:07:29,267 --> 00:07:30,433
Red, please.

127
00:07:38,633 --> 00:07:40,700
Pick up! He's not answering!

128
00:07:43,167 --> 00:07:45,000
He's not answering!

129
00:07:45,133 --> 00:07:47,300
What if my suspicion is correct?

130
00:07:47,433 --> 00:07:48,467
Don't panic yet.

131
00:07:48,633 --> 00:07:49,733
We don't know yet
if he's in the car.

132
00:07:49,867 --> 00:07:52,533
Well, we have to make sure
that my son is safe!

133
00:07:55,867 --> 00:07:59,300
If you need to talk to Eden,
then do so.

134
00:07:59,433 --> 00:08:01,267
I just want to make sure
that Red is safe.

135
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,133
Rina, I can't do that!

136
00:08:03,267 --> 00:08:04,500
I can't talk to Eden.

137
00:08:04,633 --> 00:08:05,867
Do you want me to end up
in jail?

138
00:08:10,433 --> 00:08:12,167
Red...

139
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:15,533
You're the only guy
who taught me how to love.

140
00:08:20,133 --> 00:08:23,433
And we shared happy memories
together.

141
00:08:25,667 --> 00:08:29,633
I don't know how to create
memories without you.

142
00:08:31,633 --> 00:08:34,500
Because I can't love
anyone else.

143
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:40,867
My life is worthless
without you.

144
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,367
Please, wake up.

145
00:08:57,333 --> 00:08:59,767
This is all your fault!

146
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:01,333
You're to blame!

147
00:09:01,467 --> 00:09:02,367
Wait a minute.

148
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:03,533
Why are you blaming me for this?

149
00:09:03,667 --> 00:09:04,967
Isn't this your plan?

150
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:07,967
You told me
to cut Lucho's car brakes!

151
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,633
Wait a minute,
are you trying to blame me?

152
00:09:09,767 --> 00:09:13,433
And don't raise your voice
at me, Zandro.

153
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:15,733
Find my son!

154
00:09:15,867 --> 00:09:16,933
That's what you should do.

155
00:09:20,267 --> 00:09:21,900
Okay, fine.

156
00:09:22,033 --> 00:09:25,667
We won't accomplish anything
by blaming each other.

157
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:28,933
I'll do anything.

158
00:09:29,067 --> 00:09:30,300
I'll find Red.

159
00:09:30,433 --> 00:09:33,433
But Rina...

160
00:09:33,567 --> 00:09:39,067
When you make a mistake,
you should own up to it.

161
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,600
You can't keep blaming me.

162
00:09:40,733 --> 00:09:42,867
Zandro, find my son.

163
00:10:08,933 --> 00:10:11,033
Looks like this is the end
of the line for us.

164
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,867
Whatever you're planning, Red...

165
00:10:17,367 --> 00:10:19,100
I'm coming with you.

166
00:10:23,133 --> 00:10:25,400
I leave it all to you.

167
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,733
My life, my heart.

168
00:10:30,033 --> 00:10:31,567
Because I love you so much.

169
00:10:37,367 --> 00:10:41,000
I will let fate decide for us,
Red.

170
00:10:42,900 --> 00:10:44,267
I'll accept
whatever fate has for us.

171
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:48,367
I'm coming with you, Red.

172
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:04,500
I love you so much, Red.

173
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:53,300
Come on, pick up!

174
00:11:56,533 --> 00:11:58,767
Come on, Red.
Come on, come on, come on.

175
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:13,633
Hey, did you go out?

176
00:12:17,933 --> 00:12:19,033
Where have you been?

177
00:12:23,167 --> 00:12:25,367
Rina, no more secrets, right?

178
00:12:26,667 --> 00:12:28,567
Don't tell me you're hiding
something from me again.

179
00:12:29,567 --> 00:12:30,867
Victor...

180
00:12:32,033 --> 00:12:33,033
it's Red.

181
00:12:35,933 --> 00:12:37,233
Boss!

182
00:12:37,367 --> 00:12:38,500
That's their car!

183
00:12:41,867 --> 00:12:42,833
Stop the car!

184
00:12:42,967 --> 00:12:43,933
I'm coming down.

185
00:16:32,267 --> 00:16:35,233
Red is not home.

186
00:16:35,367 --> 00:16:37,333
Red left?

187
00:16:39,467 --> 00:16:42,200
Well, Emma just told me
that Red left.

188
00:16:42,367 --> 00:16:43,967
He's not here.

189
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:50,000
I suspect that he went
to Lucho's house to see Eden.

190
00:16:50,133 --> 00:16:52,833
So Red left,
and you didn't tell me?

191
00:16:54,667 --> 00:16:56,233
I didn't want to bother you
anymore.

192
00:16:56,367 --> 00:16:58,300
You were resting, Victor.

193
00:16:58,433 --> 00:16:59,600
You know what?

194
00:16:59,733 --> 00:17:01,100
This is our son, Rina.

195
00:17:02,133 --> 00:17:03,200
We've lost a son already.

196
00:17:03,333 --> 00:17:05,400
I don't want this
to happen again.

197
00:17:05,533 --> 00:17:07,300
So, what happened?

198
00:17:07,433 --> 00:17:08,500
Where is Red?

199
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,633
Come on, come on, come on.

200
00:17:23,767 --> 00:17:24,733
Pick up.

201
00:17:27,900 --> 00:17:29,267
Come on, Red.

202
00:17:31,867 --> 00:17:32,833
Come on!

203
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,267
Eden, you have to fight.

204
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,467
Do not give up.

205
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,667
Don't leave me.

206
00:19:28,833 --> 00:19:31,133
Please, don't leave me.

207
00:19:31,267 --> 00:19:33,000
Eden. Eden, dear.

208
00:19:33,133 --> 00:19:34,200
Eden!

209
00:19:40,567 --> 00:19:41,433
Eden!

210
00:19:41,567 --> 00:19:42,833
Ma'am, you have to stay here.

211
00:19:42,967 --> 00:19:44,833
You can't come inside.

212
00:19:44,967 --> 00:19:46,900
Please take care of my daughter.

213
00:19:47,033 --> 00:19:49,133
Please, do everything you can
to help her.

214
00:19:49,267 --> 00:19:51,500
I'm begging you.

215
00:19:51,633 --> 00:19:53,667
Yes, Ma'am.
We'll do everything we can.

216
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:54,767
Excuse me.

217
00:19:56,033 --> 00:19:57,300
Lucho.

218
00:19:59,033 --> 00:20:00,300
Come on, Red.

219
00:20:08,133 --> 00:20:09,033
Hey...

220
00:20:10,067 --> 00:20:11,000
are you leaving?

221
00:20:12,033 --> 00:20:13,900
Yes, I'll go to Lucho's house.

222
00:20:14,033 --> 00:20:15,933
I'm going to find Red.

223
00:20:16,067 --> 00:20:17,933
But he's not there.

224
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:23,500
Hello?

225
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:28,500
Yes.

226
00:20:28,633 --> 00:20:29,733
That's me.

227
00:20:29,867 --> 00:20:30,900
I'm his father.

228
00:20:32,133 --> 00:20:33,800
What?

229
00:20:33,933 --> 00:20:34,967
What hospital?

230
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:44,667
I can't bear to lose Eden!

231
00:20:46,700 --> 00:20:48,533
Stop crying.
You need to calm down.

232
00:20:48,667 --> 00:20:49,900
Calm down? How can I calm down?

233
00:20:50,033 --> 00:20:52,267
My daughter's life is in danger!

234
00:20:53,900 --> 00:20:54,867
Please, stop.

235
00:20:56,733 --> 00:20:58,267
This is not the right time
for this.

236
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:01,300
There's no right time
to feel like this!

237
00:21:01,433 --> 00:21:06,233
Because I can't control
how and when I'll get hurt!

238
00:21:06,367 --> 00:21:07,433
I know. Calm down.

239
00:21:09,867 --> 00:21:11,200
My Eden.

240
00:21:12,633 --> 00:21:14,000
My Eden.

241
00:21:17,533 --> 00:21:18,600
Excuse me.

242
00:21:18,733 --> 00:21:20,600
Hello. Hi...

243
00:21:20,733 --> 00:21:24,000
We've already transferred
both patients to the ICU.

244
00:21:24,133 --> 00:21:26,567
We've done
an emergency operation

245
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:29,000
for Miss Eden Sta. Maria.

246
00:21:29,133 --> 00:21:32,300
The good news is there's
no internal organ damage.

247
00:21:32,433 --> 00:21:33,667
The bad news is...

248
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:35,000
she's not stable yet.

249
00:21:35,133 --> 00:21:36,800
So is the other patient.

250
00:21:38,833 --> 00:21:41,933
I'll be straight
and firm with you, okay?

251
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:45,000
She and the other patient
are still in critical condition.

252
00:21:45,133 --> 00:21:48,633
We still need to observe them
for the next 24 hours...

253
00:21:48,767 --> 00:21:49,933
unfortunately.

254
00:21:50,067 --> 00:21:53,967
But she will wake up, right?

255
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:57,700
I cannot promise you anything
yet.

256
00:21:57,833 --> 00:22:01,200
But what I can promise
is we will do our best for them.

257
00:22:01,333 --> 00:22:03,333
As of now,
we've done everything we could.

258
00:22:03,467 --> 00:22:05,733
All we can do now is hope
and pray that they'll improve.

259
00:22:05,867 --> 00:22:07,000
Okay?

260
00:22:07,133 --> 00:22:08,633
- Please, excuse me.
- Doc, please do everything

261
00:22:08,767 --> 00:22:10,267
you can to help them.

262
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:18,367
I heard
that these two are lovers.

263
00:22:18,500 --> 00:22:20,833
Unfortunately,
their families hate each other.

264
00:22:20,967 --> 00:22:22,467
That's why they tried
to run away.

265
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:23,567
Yen!

266
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:28,033
- Red!
- Yen!

267
00:22:28,167 --> 00:22:30,033
- Red!
- Yen!

268
00:22:30,167 --> 00:22:32,433
Victor! What's going on?

269
00:22:32,567 --> 00:22:34,067
Is this going to happen again?

270
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,867
Are we going to lose
another child?

271
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,500
Victor, I can't bear
to lose him!

272
00:22:38,767 --> 00:22:41,967
You should have thought of that
when we still had Red.

273
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:43,600
You shouldn't have let
your hatred

274
00:22:43,733 --> 00:22:44,767
and revenge consume you.

275
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:46,733
Please, God,
I will change my ways.

276
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:51,100
I will let go of the hatred
in my heart.

277
00:22:52,367 --> 00:22:54,633
I will surrender everything
to you, God.

278
00:22:54,767 --> 00:22:57,367
Please don't take my daughter
away from me.

279
00:22:57,500 --> 00:22:59,933
I'm begging you.

280
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:02,633
Red, I'm glad you're here.

281
00:23:04,067 --> 00:23:06,967
I'm happy that I can touch you
and hug you.

282
00:23:07,100 --> 00:23:08,833
Yen, like what I promised you.

283
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:11,433
We'll be staying on this island.

284
00:23:11,567 --> 00:23:15,333
We'll stay
where everything started.
